ygData.messageBody:

> Date: Sat, 07 Sep 2002 19:21:16 -0000
> From: "mouse_the_kender"

> Subject: Newbie Dwarf Paladin
>
> Hello all, I am a brand newbie, and am wondering if
> there are any
> other dwarf Pally's out there. and if so, what are
> the important
> quests for low level.....Thanks
>
> Mouse


best thing to do is to look up the newbie quests.
Great way to get you some armor to wear while you are
first starting to make a name for yourself. BTW what
server? I may have some stuff in the bank that will
help you out. Can let you borrow them til you get
better. Check out EQAtlas and buy alot of paper.
Look up the dwarven city and there is a link to the
quests that can be done for not only newbies but I
still do alot of the other quests there. So look
those up and they can be of great help. I myself
don't play a pally, so I can't tell you much about the
class, but can point you in the direction.

Zindi
Grand Master Drunken Chanter of Greenhall
